         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Your Honour, ¶  ¶ I have the honour to send to you the certificate by which the local Society for the promotion of all the natural sciences has elected you as an ordinary member. ¶  At the same time I...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">76.12.07</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Otto von Heusinger</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M106, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">Document is a printed form letter with handwritten salutation, valediction, date and address lines inserted in spaces left in the text.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Ew. Hochwohlgeboren</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>habe ich die Ehre das Diplom zu übersenden, wodurch Sie die hiesige Gesellschaft zur Beförderung der gesammten Natur-Wissenschaften zu ihrem ordentlichen Mitgliede ernennt, und Sie zugleich gehorsamst zu bitten, Ihre an die Gesellschaft zu sendenden Briefe, Abhandlungen oder andere Gegenstände an mich zu senden, und auf der Addresse gefälligst hinzuzusetzen:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">"Für die Gesellschaft zur Beförderung der gesammten Natur-Wissenschaften."</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit der grössten Hochachtung habe ich die Ehre zu seyn</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ew. Hochwohlgeboren</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Marburg, den 7 ten December</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>1876</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Der beständige Sekretär der Gesellschaft,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>Dr O. v. Heusinger</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Sr Hochwohlgeboren</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Freiherrn Dr Ferdinand von Müller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">(Australien)</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Your Honour,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honour to send to you the certificate by which the local Society for the promotion of all the natural sciences has elected you as an ordinary member.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See Gesellschaft zur Beförderung der gesammten Naturwissenschaften in Marburg to M, 1 December 1876.</p>
               </note> At the same time I beg to request that you will kindly send any letters, contributions or other objects to me and add on the address:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">'Gesellschaft zur Beförderung der gesammten Natur-Wissenschaften'.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">The </seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; background-color: #ffffff; ">Sitzungsberichte der Gesellschaft zur Beförderung der Gesamten Naturwissenschaften zu Marburg</seg>, 1877, p. 106, records the receipt of a copy of M's<seg style="background-color: #ffffff; "> </seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; background-color: #ffffff; ">Select plants</seg>
                     <seg style="background-color: #ffffff; "> </seg>(B76.12.04).</p>
                  <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With the greatest respect</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honour to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your Honour,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>the permanent Secretary of the Society</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dr O. von Heusinger.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Marburg, 7 December 1876</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">His Honour</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron Dr Ferdinand von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">(Australia)</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
